{"id":37303,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/37303","type":2,"name":"伏 鉄砲娘の捕物帳","name_cn":"伏 铁炮娘的捕物帐","summary":"改编自日本小说家 樱庭一树笔下作品《伏－贋作・里见八犬传－》，今年秋季将推出动画电影《伏 铁砲娘的捕物帐》。\r\n\r\n於 2010 年 11 月於文艺春秋出版社发表的《伏－贋作・里见八犬传－》（中文版由台湾角川代理发行），故事以知名的《里见八犬传》为发想，一群被称之为「伏」的歹徒，频频在江户犯下兇恶的罪行。年纪虽小却十分厉害的少女猎师「滨路」，与其兄浪人道节一同狩猎这些名为「伏」的犬人。而形迹可疑跟踪在这位少女身后的，正是《南总里见八犬传》作者、瀧泽马琴之子，滨路为了追击一匹伏，迷失在江户的地下道中，这是一个狩猎与被狩猎的故事……。\r\n\r\n樱庭一树过去曾发表《不适合少女的职业》、《糖果子弹（A Lollypop or A Bullet）》、《赤朽叶家的传说》等许多获奖并受到好评的作品，并以《我的男人》一作获得第 138 届得直木赏，而其笔下作品《GOSICK》也推出有电视动画作品。","eps":[{"id":263196,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/263196","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"2012-10-20","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":311,"count":{"1":1,"2":2,"3":7,"4":11,"5":38,"6":90,"7":120,"8":39,"9":1,"10":2},"score":6.4},"rank":4359,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/25/ad/37303_xavM2.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/25/ad/37303_xavM2.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/25/ad/37303_xavM2.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/25/ad/37303_xavM2.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/25/ad/37303_xavM2.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":226,"collect":427,"doing":11,"on_hold":21,"dropped":17},"crt":[{"id":16373,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/16373","name":"浜路","name_cn":"","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/d5/35/16373_crt_DDDhx.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/d5/35/16373_crt_DDDhx.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/d5/35/16373_crt_DDDhx.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d5/35/16373_crt_DDDhx.jpg"},"comment":0,"collects":1,"info":{"alias":{"romaji":"Hamaji"},"gender":"女"},"actors":[{"id":5118,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/5118","name":"寿美菜子","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c5/1c/5118_prsn_6E8HL.jpg?r=1421324719","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/c5/1c/5118_prsn_6E8HL.jpg?r=1421324719","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/c5/1c/5118_prsn_6E8HL.jpg?